A sugar pill can actually reduce pain, but how?

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:06,000
It's not just in your head.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:08,400
The placebo effect is real biology.

4
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:12,000
When we expect relief, our brains release natural opioids.

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,400
Clinical studies show that context and expectation shape our pain perception.

6
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:22,800
So, the next time you hear 'it's all in your head', remember: your brain changes reality.

